{"tid":319501,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇戒甜人士入黎講下？","createTime":"2017-07-13T00:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T14:34:11.000Z","uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2d4038c2db19cbc8de883a9b3dd35e88440826","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"我自己就一直覺得甜野冇好，又肥又加速衰老<br />\n所以都可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出街食飯飲既野可以走都會走甜<br />\n買野飲都唔會選盒裝枝裝有糖份既野<br />\n呢個做法我都持續左三四年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終都戒唔到甜品類既野<br />\n尤其係雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地究竟點戒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39805b2d8e7652ef97ae37685e0d4a04b28dab27","tid":319501,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己就一直覺得甜野冇好，又肥又加速衰老<br />\n所以都可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出街食飯飲既野可以走都會走甜<br />\n買野飲都唔會選盒裝枝裝有糖份既野<br />\n呢個做法我都持續左三四年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終都戒唔到甜品類既野<br />\n尤其係雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地究竟點戒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒甜會變你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cfdbc85a533ca0eeb1812d9bbdc178de8f1e62","tid":319501,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:22:24.000Z","msg":"加速衰老<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a24a7a972f3ed4640873814c54d61e3803f83f","tid":319501,"uid":16120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:25:26.000Z","msg":"不如索性戒埋白飯"},{"pid":"51de936e93adffa8146dbd4fca0ee123b80b6e0c","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加速衰老<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網睇過<br />\n砂糖係會催老，增加皺紋架"},{"pid":"ee613a868ca1e4be67d355afffe508b25fc61158","tid":319501,"uid":85063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我自己就一直覺得甜野冇好，又肥又加速衰老<br />\n所以都可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出街食飯飲既野可以走都會走甜<br />\n買野飲都唔會選盒裝枝裝有糖份既野<br />\n呢個做法我都持續左三四年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終都戒唔到甜品類既野<br />\n尤其係雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地究竟點戒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒到一飲甜野就喉嚨唔舒服"},{"pid":"307ad2f4387c9eaa764033b203bb10c35fb772e0","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如索性戒埋白飯</blockquote><br />\n我真係戒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚冇食<br />\n只係中午會食一兩啖<br />\n因為屋企人煮飯，唔方便叫佢地煮其他代替品，所以戒唔哂<br />\n遲下自己搬出黎住我會慢慢試下用邊隻代替白飯係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4ef7a0c820bb1e63fdc467e72b0c520b1064ed","tid":319501,"uid":71219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:38:09.000Z","msg":"戒到飯戒唔到雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n零食係最易戒既野 唔去買 行超市唔行去個邊就得"},{"pid":"a17354a946915b2bd7e48028f26ee7df7b990d76","tid":319501,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"你一日三餐通常食咩？<br />\n當你走麵包鋪買個鹹包其實都落左唔小糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d8450f67d06c9bb773573de2c90865f550758b","tid":319501,"uid":75221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"戎過一年，身體真係好左。本來長期咳又好易感冒，不過我有長期做運動加唔食甜野一年，身體就好左好多。<br />\n可能心理作用。"},{"pid":"08be7be1c21f9ae390ca3fef4953987fdd01a950","tid":319501,"uid":16120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如索性戒埋白飯</blockquote><br />\n我真係戒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚冇食<br />\n只係中午會食一兩啖<br />\n因為屋企人煮飯，唔方便叫佢地煮其他代替品，所以戒唔哂<br />\n遲下自己搬出黎住我會慢慢試下用邊隻代替白飯係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒糖/甜 個行為本身好<br />\n但個理由就好撚on9<br />\n要夾硬講既<br />\n理論上抖氣都會氧化/老化啦<br />\n咁你係咪唔撚抖氣?<br />\n<br />\n飯 你腸胃ok 既<br />\n咪試下隔日紅米之類個D"},{"pid":"d4e34d15371762010d9046665bbb48b023a12c71","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒到飯戒唔到雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n零食係最易戒既野 唔去買 行超市唔行去個邊就得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同fd出完街 甜品環節我拒絕唔到<br />\n同埋我真係好撚鍾意食軟雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490620c321e049a814229342201aa654e0d58414","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你一日三餐通常食咩？<br />\n當你走麵包鋪買個鹹包其實都落左唔小糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早餐食麥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中午夜晚屋企煮既<br />\n有時食麥皮食到覺得dry先會出街買 茶記嗰d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10c56160e95d61b2761eeb66862134cd41d2b6e","tid":319501,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"又唔能夠全戒嘅<br />\n糖分必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdedb249ed9e8cb4128a7dcc464ec329f561200","tid":319501,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T01:20:54.000Z","msg":"因為健身，基本上可以避免嘅糖都唔會食，一日可能最多得幾g糖落到肚，跟住先排大學考試，果日要由朝考到夜，朝早啪咗包旺仔qq糖，跟住成日都好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼碌到勁大"},{"pid":"8d0577bf3e15d44840533e37948d45c3fde346f3","tid":319501,"uid":64398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:11:24.000Z","msg":"出街食飯哎走甜即係飲涷野啦, 飲涷野已經唔洗旨意身體會好"},{"pid":"8bf1367e26971f848b408018a307b53cf548361f","tid":319501,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"少糖，乜都少糖就得<br />\n買野飲留意糖份<br />\n遲早就慣<br />\n<br />\n而家飲杯貢茶都覺得好甜好想嘔，微糖咗會好好多"},{"pid":"95a8af0154a00c44925bb074054941eca0d654dc","tid":319501,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少糖，乜都少糖就得<br />\n買野飲留意糖份<br />\n遲早就慣<br />\n<br />\n而家飲杯貢茶都覺得好甜好想嘔，微糖咗會好好多</blockquote><br />\n當然少糖要計埋你吸收咗幾多糖分，控制一日幾多羹糖<br />\n<br />\n一羹糖4g，世衛標準好似一日唔超過4羹糖<br />\n就咁計飲野，你買包檸檬茶都已經10g x 2.5 = 25g ／4g= 6.25羹<br />\n一包已經超咗，都幾恐佈<br />\n計埋你其他野食，真係唔少野<br />\n<br />\n所以，慢慢計吓計吓，你就會有意識控制糖<br />\n就算唔計，食到咁上下你都會比之前更有意識，去停止再吸收糖分<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆啦"},{"pid":"31509a8c6f1c4e47bd1a104f47b87b853ee4e24a","tid":319501,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戎過一年，身體真係好左。本來長期咳又好易感冒，不過我有長期做運動加唔食甜野一年，身體就好左好多。<br />\n可能心理作用。</blockquote><br />\n係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021fb69e34996f2e698a7224ce62d297d348d9a1","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如索性戒埋白飯</blockquote><br />\n我真係戒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚冇食<br />\n只係中午會食一兩啖<br />\n因為屋企人煮飯，唔方便叫佢地煮其他代替品，所以戒唔哂<br />\n遲下自己搬出黎住我會慢慢試下用邊隻代替白飯係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒糖/甜 個行為本身好<br />\n但個理由就好撚on9<br />\n要夾硬講既<br />\n理論上抖氣都會氧化/老化啦<br />\n咁你係咪唔撚抖氣?<br />\n<br />\n飯 你腸胃ok 既<br />\n咪試下隔日紅米之類個D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n始終甜野冇好，就算唔講老，都會肥啦！<br />\n<br />\n我都係諗住用糙米呀紅米嗰d黎代替白米<br />\n白米基本上都冇哂營養價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係我地習慣食<br />\n不過痴屋企人食，又廢事叫佢地煲多次米就係為左就我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2371a9873d92ef9db768cd577f2276fd6d52bdd9","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔能夠全戒嘅<br />\n糖分必須<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得日常好多野都已經有糖 <br />\n例如樓上有講 麵包都有<br />\n所以覺得應該要戒d好明顯高糖既野"},{"pid":"dd8fd2c6fed77d2f5cb01808faf9ca0965820cce","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少糖，乜都少糖就得<br />\n買野飲留意糖份<br />\n遲早就慣<br />\n<br />\n而家飲杯貢茶都覺得好甜好想嘔，微糖咗會好好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時飲下隔離嗌既 冇少甜既野  一啖都覺得好甜好辛苦<br />\n但只限飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雪糕我係唔會覺得甜"},{"pid":"77f6f0e5819293099c0852e6cf42027d63157f78","tid":319501,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:54:20.000Z","msg":"無戒過<br />\n因為天生唔中意食甜嘢<br />\n啲frd問點忍到十幾年唔飲汽水<br />\n明明我就憎飲甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e6e12552d896551444cc511b665b8bb4368942","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>少糖，乜都少糖就得<br />\n買野飲留意糖份<br />\n遲早就慣<br />\n<br />\n而家飲杯貢茶都覺得好甜好想嘔，微糖咗會好好多</blockquote><br />\n當然少糖要計埋你吸收咗幾多糖分，控制一日幾多羹糖<br />\n<br />\n一羹糖4g，世衛標準好似一日唔超過4羹糖<br />\n就咁計飲野，你買包檸檬茶都已經10g x 2.5 = 25g ／4g= 6.25羹<br />\n一包已經超咗，都幾恐佈<br />\n計埋你其他野食，真係唔少野<br />\n<br />\n所以，慢慢計吓計吓，你就會有意識控制糖<br />\n就算唔計，食到咁上下你都會比之前更有意識，去停止再吸收糖分<br />\n<br />\n持之以恆啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係啊！<br />\n我當年開始意識到要戒糖<br />\n就係因為睇到電視講成年人每日吸取糖份既標準<br />\n然後就開始留意下d飲品既糖份<br />\n覺得超得好撚誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  決定要戒"},{"pid":"572bda80ce7d973c30f222953b72b5c445ada658","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T03:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無戒過<br />\n因為天生唔中意食甜嘢<br />\n啲frd問點忍到十幾年唔飲汽水<br />\n明明我就憎飲甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁呢d天生 冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd65bef2516af77d94a9781e90a0c560073b0a3b","tid":319501,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"細個冇糖份攝取呢個概念<br />\n所以成日飲汽水，一日一罐<br />\n後來大個左開始睇營養標籤先發覺巿面d野飲可以好高糖，覺得好肥自然少掂<br />\n而甜品好似蛋糕、糖水、雪糕呢d通常食落太甜，好膩，加上本身自己都唔好甜野<br />\n唔需要特別戒都會避開"},{"pid":"be342ba5284f9c371cf1bb3989726e022caaba38","tid":319501,"uid":29983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"當你要戒某樣嘢，你會同自己講''唔可以''<br />\n但咁樣會好容易俾自己有藉口，例如''有得同fd食甜品好難得，我食埋今次就唔食''<br />\n<br />\n所以你可以試吓改變心態，同自己講：我唔食甜嘢<br />\n等自己冇藉口再食<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">:o 我都喺上網學返嚟，不過仲未實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"d82fd9b42a4d9eed389b4c73488f448735fff106","tid":319501,"uid":97299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你要戒某樣嘢，你會同自己講''唔可以''<br />\n但咁樣會好容易俾自己有藉口，例如''有得同fd食甜品好難得，我食埋今次就唔食''<br />\n<br />\n所以你可以試吓改變心態，同自己講：我唔食甜嘢<br />\n等自己冇藉口再食<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">:o 我都喺上網學返嚟，不過仲未實行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n我都覺，&ldquo;唔可以&rdquo;好似逼自己咁<br />\n&ldquo;根本唔食&rdquo;就暗示其實自己本身冇興趣"},{"pid":"d0886b18068404522c7a2b32e78ebc29c5446bde","tid":319501,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"飲野可以介<br />\n但係雪糕真係介唔撚到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b5fb882c45746796f90519127943e54d790c67","tid":319501,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"糖份係有令人快樂既成份，完全戒晒個人會燥"},{"pid":"8f949a451e1183e7852e74a9a9d650d366b98f98","tid":319501,"uid":71219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T04:38:09.000Z","msg":"得閒食下完全冇問題喎 <br />\n我唔信得閒食下會影響到身體健康<br />\n成世人流流長 唔通真係完全唔食自己鍾意既野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc8b41074e3fd4aed706b9da4fa19463cddd22d","tid":319501,"uid":1248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>糖份係有令人快樂既成份，完全戒晒個人會燥</blockquote><br />\n唔關事<br />\n你血糖穩定根本冇影響，仲會好精神添<br />\n你講既情況係個d血糖會大幅度升升跌跌<br />\n戒糖初期就係會咁"},{"pid":"a5add72c1026e4df2d24f4c853519ddda4e09e23","tid":319501,"uid":32132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"試下食藜麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都介左甜好耐 淨係飲熱水"},{"pid":"2c50a47e2064209d62a1a04ef0914ba8ddb53c1d","tid":319501,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下食藜麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都介左甜好耐 淨係飲熱水</blockquote><br />\n我都有聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我日日係office都飲大量暖水<br />\n不過出街食飯好少嗌熱野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想戒埋凍飲啊"},{"pid":"a15c92cb483b5e31afbd6ef7ca9b932eccb578ea","tid":319501,"uid":44798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:31:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d8b3433980238b6669d2c3fe4def423ffe4d692","tid":319501,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:43:38.000Z","msg":"我由戒零食同埋盡量叫熱飲自己落少D糖開始<br />\n慢慢就會愈食愈少唔鍾意甜野<br />\n而家連朱古力都係平均半年先食一次<br />\n不過有時都會唔覺意食一次雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ae2a135f7fcc93b8cdb066b09af5e759451617","tid":319501,"uid":32132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下食藜麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都介左甜好耐 淨係飲熱水</blockquote><br />\n我都有聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我日日係office都飲大量暖水<br />\n不過出街食飯好少嗌熱野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想戒埋凍飲啊</blockquote><br />\n戒埋凍飲就fit 因為我都坐office 如果唔喺食呢part入手就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0301873e8c0dd8b5b7534c5583d4ed35a5a7483","tid":319501,"uid":47095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"出街食飯真係完全唔會嗌甜野飲 但身邊啲fd唔嗌檸茶奶茶好似會死咁 我真係完全唔明<br />\n但我戒唔撚到啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c94a819855bb1f4ee3a425d3cfdd04320e1381b","tid":319501,"uid":32132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街食飯真係完全唔會嗌甜野飲 但身邊啲fd唔嗌檸茶奶茶好似會死咁 我真係完全唔明<br />\n但我戒唔撚到啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同你一撚樣"},{"pid":"cb9246753954ddf9ee0898d6ec71a79748794c01","tid":319501,"uid":73068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"其實我都好想戒，但係白飯、麵包日日都要食點戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dea3c5c9644cbf6fa687d13aadb74f5a1b6e4f3","tid":319501,"uid":73068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:49:25.000Z","msg":"牛肉、牛奶、甜食、凍飲全部都應該戒，但係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2556d79d7c6bf40a54caf3309e434bcf5e7783","tid":319501,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:11:04.000Z","msg":"搵代替品"},{"pid":"0508d0179bb72e0cd3180f802e83f56bc1512d82","tid":319501,"uid":88394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街食飯真係完全唔會嗌甜野飲 但身邊啲fd唔嗌檸茶奶茶好似會死咁 我真係完全唔明<br />\n但我戒唔撚到啤酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檸茶奶茶可以走甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e903b1d903586e060c7e4fe07b05874cb663ed99","tid":319501,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"如果係女仔<br />\n戒糖其中一個動力就係糖食得多，個樣會老啲殘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5bd8f8ef0efd797fc0b2775950b60144a534f1","tid":319501,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"以前D人邊會食到咁多額外加既糖<br />\n本身食物裡面既糖都夠用<br />\n多餘既糖只會破壞皮膚,搞壞身體<br />\n雖然都係咁,我都係戒唔到糖"},{"pid":"1eb6d1bd0495dd91301e97c4be6ea174522d7b5a","tid":319501,"uid":73068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"咁生果你地食唔食？"},{"pid":"ebb0fb94d5e0f34535bfc31786e3cbc0622ff050","tid":319501,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"十穀米<br />\n多食生果<br />\n椰棗"},{"pid":"5c20df5af90314d5be72262a6720b2041edae11b","tid":319501,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"夏天好難戒汽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f7d53dcb9903f434321572d735dc5a3da56785","tid":319501,"uid":10702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"本身想去食雪條 都1516 睇完個po不了"},{"pid":"2ba048ea69745ff77a17082f10e0da9af9ed67c5","tid":319501,"uid":128277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"可以唔食飯唔食雪糕唔食糖唔飲有糖份既飲品<br />\n但係戒唔到朱古力！！！！油+糖先至係萬惡之源！！！！好痛苦"}]}